Class ArchiveUnitRefList

  • Object
    • DataObjectPackageElement
      • ArchiveUnitRefList

  • public class ArchiveUnitRefList
extends DataObjectPackageElement
    The Class ArchiveUnitList.

    Class for managing list of child ArchiveUnits either by id or by object reference. Those two modes are useful at different moments of process (import -< ID, ArchiveTransfer fusion -< objects...).

    It keeps inner two lists, one of ids and one of ArchiveUnit objects. At a given moment only one list is defined the other one is null. So if you need for example to change ArchiveUnits ID, you have before to force all ArchiveUnitRefList in object reference mode by reading the object references list.
